---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Privacy Policy — Zebra"
	description="Privacy policy for Zebra, a symptom tracker for POTS, EDS, and Fibromyalgia."
>
	<div class="legal-shell">
		<a class="legal-back" href="/">← Back to Zebra</a>
		<div class="legal-card">
			<p class="eyebrow">Privacy</p>
			<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="legal-updated">Last updated: May 14, 2026</p>

			<p>
				Zebra is being built to help people track symptoms, flares, orthostatic vitals, and
				related health information. If you join the waitlist or contact us, this page explains
				what information we collect and how we use it.
			</p>

			<h2>What we collect</h2>
			<p>
				If you join the waitlist, we may collect your email address and any information you
				voluntarily include in the form.
			</p>

			<h2>How we use it</h2>
			<p>
				We use this information to send updates about Zebra, invite people to test the app, and
				reply to questions or requests.
			</p>

			<h2>How we share information</h2>
			<p>
				We do not sell your personal information. We may use third-party services such as form,
				email, hosting, or analytics providers to operate the site and manage communications.
			</p>

			<h2>Data retention</h2>
			<p>
				We keep waitlist or contact information only as long as reasonably necessary to operate
				the waitlist, communicate with interested users, and manage the launch.
			</p>

			<h2>Your choices</h2>
			<p>
				You can request that we update or delete your information by contacting us at
				<a href="mailto:hello@getzebra.app">hello@getzebra.app</a>.
			</p>

			<h2>Medical information</h2>
			<p>
				Zebra is not a medical provider and this website does not offer medical advice,
				diagnosis, or treatment.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
